Description: pksensi implements the global sensitivity analysis workflow to investigate the parameter uncertainty and sensitivity in pharmacokinetic (PK) models, especially the physiologically-based pharmacokinetic (PBPK) model with multivariate outputs. The package also provide some functions to check the convergence and sensitivity of model parameters.   
